# Open Blooms Email Design Guide
## Klaviyo Email Design System | Visual Specifications Only

**Based on Open Blooms Brand Guidelines**  
Last Updated: December 15, 2025

---

## Table of Contents

1. Email Canvas & Container Specifications
2. Typography System for Email
