## 1. Email Canvas & Container Specifications

### Container Dimensions

**Email Width:**
- Maximum: `600px` (standard email width)
- Minimum: `320px` (mobile)
- Content max-width: `560px` (safe zone with 20px padding)

**Email Padding:**
```css
/* Desktop */
padding-left: 30px;
padding-right: 30px;

/* Mobile (<480px) */
padding-left: 20px;
padding-right: 20px;
```

**Background Colors:**
- Email body: `#FFFFFF` (white)
- Alternate sections: `#F5F5F5` (light gray)
- Never use more than 2 background colors in email body

**Safe Zones:**
- Keep all critical CTAs within `560px` width
- Minimum 20px from container edges on mobile
- Minimum 40px from top/bottom of email

---

## 2. Typography System for Email

### Font Stack

```css
font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 
             Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
```

### Font Size Scale

**Display/Hero Headlines:**
```css
/* Desktop */
font-size: 42px - 48px;
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.2;
letter-spacing: 0.05em;
text-transform: uppercase; /* For brand headlines */

/* Mobile */
font-size: 32px - 36px;
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.2;
```

**H1 Headers:**
```css
/* Desktop */
font-size: 32px - 36px;
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.3;

/* Mobile */
font-size: 28px - 32px;
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.3;
```

**H2 Headers:**
```css
/* Desktop */
font-size: 28px - 32px;
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.3;

/* Mobile */
font-size: 24px - 28px;
font-weight: 700;
line-height: 1.3;
```

**H3 Subheaders:**
```css
/* Desktop */
font-size: 20px - 24px;
font-weight: 600;
line-height: 1.4;

/* Mobile */
font-size: 18px - 20px;
font-weight: 600;
line-height: 1.4;
```

**Body Text:**
```css
/* Desktop */
font-size: 16px - 18px;
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.6;
color: #000000;

/* Mobile */
font-size: 16px; /* Never below 16px */
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.6;
```

**Small Text (Footer, Legal):**
```css
/* Desktop */
font-size: 14px;
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.5;
color: #666666;

/* Mobile */
font-size: 13px; /* Minimum */
font-weight: 400;
line-height: 1.5;
```

### Text Alignment Rules

- Headlines: Center or left-align
- Body copy: Left-align (improves readability)
- CTAs: Center-align
- Footer: Center or left-align

### Case Usage

- Hero headlines: ALL CAPS or Title Case
- Section headers: Title Case
- Body text: Sentence case
- CTAs: Title Case ("Shop Now", "View Collection")

---

## 3. Color Palette for Email

### Primary Colors

**Black**
```css
color: #000000;
```
- Usage: Primary text, headlines, buttons
- Weight: Headlines (700), body (400)

**White**
```css
color: #FFFFFF;
```
- Usage: Background, button text on dark buttons
- Text on images: Use white with dark overlay

### Background Colors

**White**
```css
background-color: #FFFFFF;
```
- Primary email background

**Light Gray**
```css
background-color: #F5F5F5;
```
- Alternate section backgrounds
- Visual separation without harsh contrast

**Medium Gray**
```css
border-color: #CCCCCC;
border-width: 1px;
```
- Borders, dividers, subtle lines

### Text Colors

**Primary Text**
```css
color: #000000;
```

**Secondary Text**
```css
color: #333333;
```

**Tertiary Text (Footer, Less Important)**
```css
color: #666666;
```

### Accent Colors (Use Sparingly)

**Red/Coral (Urgency)**
```css
color: #E63946;
```
- Sale badges, urgent CTAs, countdown elements
- Maximum: 1-2 uses per email

**Green (Fresh/New)**
```css
color: #4A7C2C;
```
- "Fresh" messaging, seasonal accents
- Occasional use for spring/nature themes

### Image Overlay

**Dark Overlay (for text readability)**
```css
background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); /* Light overlay */
background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Medium overlay */
background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Heavy overlay */
```

---

## 4. Button & CTA Design Specs

### Primary Button

**Visual Specifications:**
```css
/* Desktop & Mobile */
background-color: #000000;
color: #FFFFFF;
font-size: 16px;
font-weight: 600;
text-align: center;
text-decoration: none;
text-transform: capitalize; /* Title Case */
padding: 14px 32px;
border-radius: 4px;
border: none;
display: inline-block;
min-width: 180px;
min-height: 44px; /* Touch target */

/* Hover state (web clients) */
background-color: #1A1A1A;
transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
```

**Mobile Adjustments:**
```css
/* Optional: Full-width on narrow screens */
@media (max-width: 400px) {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
}
```

### Secondary Button

**Visual Specifications:**
```css
background-color: transparent;
color: #000000;
font-size: 16px;
font-weight: 600;
text-align: center;
text-decoration: none;
text-transform: capitalize;
padding: 12px 28px;
border-radius: 4px;
border: 2px solid #000000;
display: inline-block;
min-height: 44px;

/* Hover state */
background-color: #000000;
color: #FFFFFF;
transition: all 0.3s ease;
```

### Text Links

**Style:**
```css
color: #000000;
text-decoration: underline;
font-weight: 500;

/* Hover */
text-decoration: none;
```

**Footer Links:**
```css
color: #666666;
text-decoration: underline;
font-size: 14px;
```

### Button Spacing

```css
/* Around buttons */
margin-top: 30px;
margin-bottom: 30px;

/* Between multiple buttons */
margin-right: 15px; /* Horizontal */
margin-bottom: 15px; /* Stacked */
```

### Button Examples

**Primary CTA:**
- Height: 44px minimum
- Width: 180px minimum (auto for longer text)
- Font: 16px, weight 600
- Color: White on black

**Secondary CTA:**
- Height: 44px minimum
- Width: Auto based on content
- Font: 16px, weight 600
- Color: Black with black border

---

## 5. Spacing & Layout Grid

### Email Grid System

**Column Structure:**
- Full width: 600px (1 column)
- Half width: 280px each (2 columns with 20px gutter)
- Third width: 186px each (3 columns with 21px gutters)

**Gutter Sizes:**
- Between columns: 20px
- Between rows: 20px
- Mobile: Reduce to 15px

### Vertical Spacing Scale

**Major Sections:**
```css
margin-top: 60px;
margin-bottom: 60px;

/* Mobile */
margin-top: 40px;
margin-bottom: 40px;
```

**Content Blocks:**
```css
margin-top: 40px;
margin-bottom: 40px;

/* Mobile */
margin-top: 30px;
margin-bottom: 30px;
```

**Between Elements:**
```css
margin-bottom: 20px; /* Paragraphs */
margin-bottom: 30px; /* After headlines */
margin-bottom: 15px; /* Between related items */
```

### Module Padding

**Header:**
```css
padding-top: 30px;
padding-bottom: 30px;

/* Mobile */
padding-top: 20px;
padding-bottom: 20px;
```

**Hero Section:**
```css
padding-top: 40px;
padding-bottom: 50px;

/* Mobile */
padding-top: 30px;
padding-bottom: 40px;
```

**Content Sections:**
```css
padding-top: 50px;
padding-bottom: 50px;

/* Mobile */
padding-top: 40px;
padding-bottom: 40px;
```

**Footer:**
```css
padding-top: 40px;
padding-bottom: 40px;

/* Mobile */
padding-top: 30px;
padding-bottom: 30px;
```

### Internal Element Padding

**Cards/Boxes:**
```css
padding: 20px;

/* Mobile */
padding: 15px;
```

**Text Containers:**
```css
padding-left: 20px;
padding-right: 20px;
```

---

## 6. Image Specifications

### File Formats

- **JPEG:** Product photos, lifestyle images, backgrounds
- **PNG:** Logos, graphics with transparency
- **GIF:** Animated elements (use sparingly)

### File Size Limits

- Individual images: **200KB maximum**
- Total email: **<1MB total** (all images combined)
- Hero images: **150-200KB**
- Product cards: **80-120KB each**
- Logos: **20-50KB**

### Image Dimensions

**Full-Width Hero:**
```
Width: 600px
Height: 400px (3:2 ratio)
Actual size: 1200px x 800px (2x for retina)
```

**Half-Width (2-Up Layout):**
```
Width: 280px
Height: 373px (3:4 ratio for products)
Actual size: 560px x 746px
```

**Third-Width (3-Up Layout):**
```
Width: 186px
Height: 248px (3:4 ratio)
Actual size: 372px x 496px
```

**Logo:**
```
Width: 150px - 180px
Height: Auto (maintain ratio)
Actual size: 300px - 360px wide
```

**Square Images:**
```
Width: 280px
Height: 280px (1:1 ratio)
Actual size: 560px x 560px
```

### Image Quality Settings

- JPEG compression: 70-85%
- PNG: Optimize with tools like TinyPNG
- Resolution: 72 DPI (web standard)
- Color space: RGB (not CMYK)

### Alt Text Requirements

**Rules:**
- Every image MUST have alt text
- Describe image clearly and concisely
- Include product name for products
- Keep under 125 characters
- Logo: alt="Open Blooms"

**Examples:**
```html
<img src="roses.jpg" alt="Red roses bouquet arrangement" />
<img src="hero.jpg" alt="Open Blooms holiday collection" />
<img src="logo.png" alt="Open Blooms" />
```

### Image Treatment

**Borders:**
```css
border: 1px solid #E5E5E5; /* Optional for product cards */
border-radius: 8px; /* Optional rounded corners */
```

**Shadows (Use Sparingly):**
```css
box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
```

---

## 7. Email Template Structures

### Template A: Hero + Product Grid

```
┌────────────────────────────────────┐
│          HEADER (Logo)             │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                    │
│       HERO IMAGE + TEXT            │
│         [CTA Button]               │
│                                    │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                    │
│    [Img]    [Img]    [Img]         │
│    Name     Name     Name          │
│    Price    Price    Price         │
│                                    │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│       [Secondary CTA]              │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│          FOOTER                    │
└────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Measurements:**
- Header: 30px padding top/bottom
- Hero: 600px x 400px image
- Grid: 3 columns @ 186px each
- Footer: 40px padding top/bottom

---

### Template B: Split Hero (Text + Image)

```
┌────────────────────────────────────┐
│          HEADER (Logo)             │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                    │
│  ┌──────────┐  ┌──────────┐        │
│  │          │  │  Hero    │        │
│  │  Text    │  │  Image   │        │
│  │  [CTA]   │  │          │        │
│  └──────────┘  └──────────┘        │
│                                    │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│        CONTENT SECTION             │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│          FOOTER                    │
└────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Measurements:**
- Each column: 280px wide
- Gutter: 20px
- Text column padding: 20px internal

---

### Template C: Stacked Content

```
┌────────────────────────────────────┐
│          HEADER (Logo)             │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│        Hero Headline               │
│        Hero Subhead                │
│        [Primary CTA]               │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│       [Product Image]              │
│       Product Name                 │
│       Description                  │
│       [Add to Cart CTA]            │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│    ┌──────┐  ┌──────┐             │
│    │Trust │  │Trust │             │
│    │Badge │  │Badge │             │
│    └──────┘  └──────┘             │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│          FOOTER                    │
└────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Measurements:**
- Full-width sections: 600px
- Trust badges: 280px each (2-up)
- Vertical spacing: 40-50px between sections

---

### Template D: Text-Heavy (Minimal Images)

```
┌────────────────────────────────────┐
│          HEADER (Logo)             │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│         Main Headline              │
│                                    │
│      Body paragraph text           │
│      continues here with           │
│      proper line spacing           │
│                                    │
│         [Primary CTA]              │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│       Subheader                    │
│                                    │
│      More body text with           │
│      spacing and formatting        │
│                                    │
├────────────────────────────────────┤
│          FOOTER                    │
└────────────────────────────────────┘
```

**Measurements:**
- Text max-width: 500px (centered)
- Paragraph spacing: 15-20px
- Section breaks: 40-50px

