## 8. Component Library with Specs

### HEADER MODULE

**Dimensions:**
```
Height: 80px - 100px
Logo width: 150px - 180px
Background: #FFFFFF
Border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5 (optional)
```

**Padding:**
```css
padding-top: 30px;
padding-bottom: 30px;

/* Mobile */
padding-top: 20px;
padding-bottom: 20px;
```

**Logo Specifications:**
- Format: PNG with transparency
- Size: 150px x auto (maintain ratio)
- Position: Center or left-align
- Link: Always to homepage
- Alt text: "Open Blooms"

---

### HERO MODULE - Full Width

**Dimensions:**
```
Image: 600px x 400px (3:2 ratio)
Actual: 1200px x 800px (2x)
Container: Full width (600px)
```

**Text Overlay:**
```css
/* Overlay background */
background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);

/* Text container */
padding: 40px;
text-align: center;

/* Mobile */
padding: 30px 20px;
```

**Typography:**
```css
/* Headline */
font-size: 42px; /* Desktop */
font-size: 32px; /* Mobile */
font-weight: 700;
color: #FFFFFF;
text-transform: uppercase;
margin-bottom: 15px;

/* Subhead */
font-size: 18px;
font-weight: 400;
color: #FFFFFF;
margin-bottom: 30px;
```

---

### PRODUCT CARD - 2-Up Layout

**Dimensions:**
```
Card width: 280px
Image: 280px x 373px (3:4 ratio)
Gutter between: 20px
```

**Card Structure:**
```css
/* Card container */
width: 280px;
background: #FFFFFF;
border: 1px solid #E5E5E5; /* Optional */
border-radius: 8px; /* Optional */

/* Image */
width: 280px;
height: 373px;
display: block;

/* Text container */
padding: 15px;

/* Product name */
font-size: 18px;
font-weight: 600;
color: #000000;
margin-bottom: 8px;

/* Price */
font-size: 16px;
font-weight: 400;
color: #333333;
margin-bottom: 15px;

/* CTA button */
/* Use secondary button specs */
```

**Mobile Behavior:**
- Stack to single column
- Maintain 280px width (or full width with padding)

---

### PRODUCT GRID - 3-Up Layout

**Dimensions:**
```
Card width: 186px each
Total: (186px × 3) + (21px × 2) = 600px
Gutter: 21px between cards
```

**Card Structure:**
```css
width: 186px;
background: #FFFFFF;

/* Image */
width: 186px;
height: 248px;
```

**Mobile Behavior:**
- Stack to single column
- Cards expand to full width with padding

