## 9. Responsive Design System

### Breakpoints

```css
/* Mobile */
@media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
  /* Single column layout */
  /* Increased touch targets */
  /* Scaled typography */
}

/* Tablet */
@media screen and (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 640px) {
  /* 2-column layouts */
  /* Moderate spacing */
}

/* Desktop */
@media screen and (min-width: 641px) {
  /* Full layout */
  /* Multi-column grids */
}
```

### Mobile Adjustments

**Typography Scale:**
```css
/* Reduce by 15-25% */
h1: 48px → 36px
h2: 32px → 28px
h3: 24px → 20px
body: 16px → 16px (maintain)
```

**Spacing Scale:**
```css
/* Reduce by 25-30% */
Section padding: 60px → 40px
Element spacing: 40px → 30px
```

**Layout Changes:**
```css
/* Multi-column → Single column */
3-up grid → Stack vertically
2-up grid → Stack vertically
Split hero → Stack (text above image)
```

**Button Adjustments:**
```css
/* Optional: Full-width on narrow */
@media (max-width: 400px) {
  button {
    width: 100%;
    display: block;
  }
}
```

### Touch Target Requirements

**Minimum Sizes:**
- Buttons: 44px × 44px
- Links: 44px × 44px (with padding)
- Tappable areas: 44px minimum in any dimension

### Image Stacking (Mobile)

**Desktop 3-up grid:**
```
[Image] [Image] [Image]
```

**Mobile stacked:**
```
[Image]
[Image]
[Image]
```

---

## 10. Technical Requirements

### HTML Structure

**Table-Based Layout:**
```html
<table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
  <tr>
    <td>Content here</td>
  </tr>
</table>
```

**Required Attributes:**
- All styles inline: `style="color: #000;"`
- All images have `alt` text
- All links have `href` attributes
- Table dimensions explicit: `width="600"`

### CSS Rules

**Allowed:**
- `font-family`, `font-size`, `font-weight`
- `color`, `background-color`
- `padding`, `margin`
- `width`, `height`
- `text-align`, `vertical-align`
- `border`, `border-radius`

**Avoid:**
- `position: absolute/fixed`
- `float`
- `flexbox`
- `grid`
- External stylesheets
- JavaScript

### Image Coding

```html
<img 
  src="https://cdn.example.com/image.jpg" 
  alt="Product description" 
  width="600" 
  height="400" 
  style="display: block; border: 0; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; height: auto;"
/>
```

**Required Attributes:**
- `src`: HTTPS URL only
- `alt`: Descriptive text
- `width` and `height`: Explicit dimensions
- `style`: Inline CSS for responsiveness

### Button Coding

```html
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
  <tr>
    <td style="background-color: #000000; border-radius: 4px; padding: 14px 32px; text-align: center;">
      <a href="https://example.com" style="color: #FFFFFF; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block;">
        Shop Now
      </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
```

### Responsive Images

```html
<img 
  src="image.jpg" 
  width="600" 
  style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; height: auto; display: block;"
/>
```

### Media Queries

```html
<style type="text/css">
  @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
    .mobile-text { font-size: 28px !important; }
    .mobile-hide { display: none !important; }
    .mobile-full { width: 100% !important; }
  }
</style>
```

### Dark Mode Support

```html
<style type="text/css">
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .darkmode-bg { background-color: #1a1a1a !important; }
    .darkmode-text { color: #ffffff !important; }
  }
</style>
```

### Klaviyo Dynamic Tags

**Personalization:**
```django
{{ first_name|default:"Friend" }}
{{ person.email }}
```

**Product Data:**
```django
{{ event.extra.ProductName }}
{{ event.extra.ItemPrice }}
{{ event.extra.ImageURL }}
```

**Conditionals:**
```django
{% if person.cart_value > 100 %}
  High-value content
{% else %}
  Standard content
{% endif %}
```

### Email Size Limits

**Total Size:**
- HTML code: <102KB (Gmail clips at 102KB)
- Total with images: <1MB
- Number of images: 10-15 maximum

**Optimization:**
- Minify HTML (remove extra spaces)
- Compress images before upload
- Combine similar styles
- Remove unnecessary code

---

## 11. Quality Checklist

### Design Verification

**Visual Check:**
- [ ] Logo present and correct size (150-180px)
- [ ] Brand colors used correctly (#000, #FFF, #F5F5F5)
- [ ] Typography matches specs (fonts, sizes, weights)
- [ ] Buttons styled correctly (primary: black/white)
- [ ] Images optimized (<200KB each)
- [ ] Alt text on all images
- [ ] Spacing consistent (40-60px sections)
- [ ] Hierarchy clear and logical

**Layout Check:**
- [ ] Container width: 600px
- [ ] Safe zones respected (20px minimum)
- [ ] Grid alignment correct
- [ ] Gutters consistent (20px)
- [ ] No elements cut off or overlapping

**Responsive Check:**
- [ ] Scales properly on mobile
- [ ] Text readable (min 16px body)
- [ ] Touch targets adequate (44px min)
- [ ] Images stack correctly
- [ ] Buttons accessible
- [ ] No horizontal scrolling

### Technical Verification

**Code Check:**
- [ ] All styles inline
- [ ] Table-based layout
- [ ] No external CSS files
- [ ] No JavaScript
- [ ] Explicit image dimensions
- [ ] HTTPS for all images
- [ ] Alt text on all images
- [ ] Responsive images coded

**Email Client Testing:**
- [ ] Gmail (web, iOS, Android)
- [ ] Apple Mail (iOS, macOS)
- [ ] Outlook (Windows, Mac, Web)
- [ ] Yahoo Mail
- [ ] Preview looks correct

**Mobile Testing:**
- [ ] iPhone (multiple sizes)
- [ ] Android (multiple sizes)
- [ ] Portrait orientation
- [ ] Landscape orientation (if relevant)

**Dark Mode Testing:**
- [ ] Logo visible in dark mode
- [ ] Text readable in dark mode
- [ ] Images display properly
- [ ] No harsh inversions

### File Size Verification

- [ ] Individual images <200KB
- [ ] Total email <1MB
- [ ] HTML code <102KB
- [ ] Images compressed
- [ ] Unnecessary code removed

### Link Verification

- [ ] All CTAs functional
- [ ] All navigation links work
- [ ] Logo links to homepage
- [ ] Social icons link correctly
- [ ] Unsubscribe link present
- [ ] View in browser link present
- [ ] UTM parameters added (if required)

### Accessibility Check

- [ ] Alt text on all images
- [ ] Color contrast meets WCAG AA (4.5:1)
- [ ] Text readable without images
- [ ] Semantic structure (headers, paragraphs)
- [ ] Links descriptive (not "click here")

---

## Quick Reference Charts

### Typography Scale

| Element | Desktop | Mobile | Weight |
|---------|---------|--------|--------|
| Hero | 42-48px | 32-36px | 700 |
| H1 | 32-36px | 28-32px | 700 |
| H2 | 28-32px | 24-28px | 700 |
| H3 | 20-24px | 18-20px | 600 |
| Body | 16-18px | 16px | 400 |
| Small | 14px | 13px | 400 |

### Spacing Scale

| Context | Desktop | Mobile |
|---------|---------|--------|
| Major sections | 60px | 40px |
| Content blocks | 40px | 30px |
| Between elements | 20-30px | 15-20px |
| Paragraph spacing | 15px | 15px |

### Image Dimensions

| Type | Width | Height | Ratio |
|------|-------|--------|-------|
| Hero | 600px | 400px | 3:2 |
| Product (2-up) | 280px | 373px | 3:4 |
| Product (3-up) | 186px | 248px | 3:4 |
| Square | 280px | 280px | 1:1 |
| Logo | 150-180px | Auto | - |

### Button Specs

| Type | BG Color | Text Color | Padding | Border |
|------|----------|------------|---------|--------|
| Primary | #000000 | #FFFFFF | 14px 32px | None |
| Secondary | Transparent | #000000 | 12px 28px | 2px solid #000 |

