## File Naming Conventions

### Images

**Format:**
```
category-descriptor-size.jpg
```

**Examples:**
```
hero-holiday-600x400.jpg
product-roses-280x373.jpg
logo-primary-180w.png
icon-trust-delivery-40x40.png
```

### Email Templates

**Format:**
```
flow-name_email-number_version.html
```

**Examples:**
```
welcome_email-1_v2.html
abandoned-cart_email-2_v1.html
holiday-campaign_dec2025.html
```

